{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"be0517fa178490d5","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\nflowchart TD\n    %% 核心终点\n    Target(\"mRNA (+)<br>蛋白质合成的通用图纸\")\n    style Target fill:#ff4d4d,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:white\n\n    %% === DNA 病毒阵营 ===\n    subgraph DNA_Family [\"DNA 病毒家族 (通常在核内)\"]\n        direction TB\n        G1[\"Group I: dsDNA<br>双链 DNA<br>(如: 腺病毒, 疱疹)\"]\n        G2[\"Group II: ssDNA<br>单链 DNA<br>(如: 细小, 圆环)\"]\n        G7[\"Group VII: dsDNA-RT<br>缺口双链 DNA<br>(如: 乙肝 HBV)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% === RNA 病毒阵营 ===\n    subgraph RNA_Family [\"RNA 病毒家族 (通常在胞质)\"]\n        direction TB\n        G3[\"Group III: dsRNA<br>双链 RNA<br>(如: 呼肠孤)\"]\n        G4[\"Group IV: (+)ssRNA<br>正义单链 RNA<br>(如: 口蹄疫, 冠状)\"]\n        G5[\"Group V: (-)ssRNA<br>反义单链 RNA<br>(如: 流感, 狂犬)\"]\n        G6[\"Group VI: ssRNA-RT<br>逆转录 RNA<br>(如: HIV, FeLV)\"]\n    end\n\n    %% === 路径连接 ===\n    \n    %% Group I: 直接转录\n    G1 -->|宿主 RNA 聚合酶 II| Target\n    \n    %% Group II: 先补双链\n    G2 -->|宿主 DNA 聚合酶| dsDNA_RF(双链中间体 RF)\n    dsDNA_RF -->|转录| Target\n\n    %% Group VII: 修复+逆转录循环\n    G7 -->|宿主修复酶| cccDNA(cccDNA<br>闭合环状 DNA)\n    cccDNA -->|转录| Target\n    Target -.->|逆转录-打包时| G7\n\n    %% Group III: 自带RdRp\n    G3 -->|自带 RdRp<br>核心内转录| Target\n\n    %% Group IV: 即插即用\n    G4 == 本身就是 ==> Target\n    Target -.->|翻译出 RdRp| Ag[\"(-)RNA 抗基因组\"]\n    Ag -.->|大量复制| G4\n\n    %% Group V: 自带RdRp\n    G5 -->|自带 RdRp<br>必须转录| Target\n\n    %% Group VI: 逆转录整合\n    G6 -->|自带 RT 酶<br>逆转录| ProDNA(前病毒 dsDNA)\n    ProDNA -->|整合酶| HostDNA(整合进宿主染色体)\n    HostDNA -->|宿主转录| Target\n\n    %% === 样式调整 ===\n    style G1 fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0\n    style G2 fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1565c0\n    style G7 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#fbc02d\n    \n    style G3 fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b\n    style G4 fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b\n    style G5 fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b\n    style G6 fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#fbc02d\n\n    style cccDNA fill:#fff59d\n    style ProDNA fill:#fff59d\n    style dsDNA_RF fill:#bbdefb\n```","x":-3120,"y":480,"width":2560,"height":2280}
	],
